Install node.js
Install ionic cli: npm install -g @ionic/cli
Navigate to ionic project directory or open project in VSCode and start terminal
Install dependencies, see list below.
Run the project in a browser: ionic serve --lab

Dependencies:
leaflet: npm i leaflet --save
leaflet types: npm i @types/leaflet -D
ionic lab: npm i -D -E @ionic/lab

NB:
I'm sorry If I missed any dependencies. 
Please also keep the map bug in mind
Please note that I have not implemented routing, change line 24 of the app.componenent.ts to view desired page. It's currently set to the trip details page. 

